name: Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac
short_description: Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac is an excellent iOS cleaner tool run on Mac OS X. It can scan and strike out almost any kind of junk files on iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch to release the clumsy storage space. Whenever you found your iPhone running slow or running out of space, you can ask help from iPhone Cleaner for Mac. It gives an effective solution to clean up your device and reclaims the lost space to speed up your iPhone and get more apps, music, movies, photos and fun in your life. Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac run on Mac OS X 10.8 or above and is compatible with iPhone, iPad, iPod touch(iOS 5-8). What is new in version 1.2.4? 1.Add product menu. 2.Restore the bug that update the up-to-date version without uninstalling the old version.
